Feature New meditation session
#As a user of the "Meditation" application I can start a new meditation session.

Scenario: User can start new meditation session
Given I open the "meditation" application
When I press "New session"
And I press "Start" button 
Then New meditation session starts

Feature Activity diagram
#As a user of the "Meditation" application I can review the activity diagram in vertical screen

Scenario: User can view activity diagram
Given I open the "meditation" application
When I press the profile Icon in the up left corner
And I press "Meditation activity diagram since"
Then the activity diagram opens in vertical screen

Feature The meditaion history
#As a user I can view my meditation history

Scenario: User can view the meditation history in the application

Given I open the "Meditation" application
When I press the profile Icon in the up left corner
And I press "Meditation history sessions"
Then I can view all my meditation history

Feature Changing user name
#As a User name can be changed in the profile page

Scenario: The User can change the user name in the profile page

Given I open the "Meditation" application
When I press the profile Icon in the up left corner
Then the profile page opens
When I click on the pen icon beside the user name
Then the table to type new user name opens
When I type the new user name
And I click "Done" button
Then the new user name is saved

Feature the meditation sesion can be paused
#The user during the meditation sesion can pasue the meditation sessions

Scenario: The user can pasue the meditation sessions
Given I open the "Meditation" application
When I press the "New session" button
Then the "New sessions" window opens
When I press start button
Then the meditaion session starts
When I press the "Pause" button
Then the meditaion session pauses
